	(text "EBYTE E22-900T30D: UART (RXD/TXD cross-connected to ESP32 in\nesp32.kicad_sch), M0/M1 mode select, AUX status, VCC from dedicated\nbuck rail (power.kicad_sch). No RF trace - module's own SMA-K\nantenna connector is mounted through the enclosure panel directly." (at 12.7 15.24 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))) (uuid "b20c2e0c-8f43-49c3-a469-730bb6cf64c1"))
